{"tid":2297343,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"27吋上4K睇唔睇到分別,同2K比明唔明顯。","createTime":"2020-11-23T08:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T07:39:54.000Z","uid":116960,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6c0d0f77e88fbe7e79556905a5f08ce9594e6c","tid":2297343,"uid":116960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:12:29.000Z","msg":"利申對眼離個MON 60CM左右,是關部機有時都做下文書野,所以你當正常咁上下連登做下文書野果種距離。<br />\n張檯好耐前買落最盡都放到32 INCH但會好撚逼,兩面喇叭要谷住放係MON後面。我其實PREFER 27吋但驚睇唔到4K同2K分別。而家煩緊點搞好,換檯的話成間ROOM LAYOUT要搞過太大工程。<br />\n做過RESEARCH我見網上話關對眼同MON距離事。我就咁離60CM左近,而家有以下幾個OPTIONS:<br />\n1. 27吋 2K 144 NT<br />\n2. 27吋 4K 60 IPS<br />\n3. 32吋 4K 60 , 但兩面喇叭要谷住放係MON後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但埋左右完全冇晒位。預做文書野睇得辛苦。(唔太PREFER)<br />\n大家點睇。有冇用家實測就咁肉眼睇得出27吋4K同32吋4K分別。順便問埋型號入咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ce8dc4c20a96d678ab5efaf744bfa408e8c5b8","tid":2297343,"uid":116960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:18:41.000Z","msg":"發錯台大家唔好回"},{"pid":"431bb87f21baed55d0d1228315b61f706f304382","tid":2297343,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:32:43.000Z","msg":"27吋 60cm咁近 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪博拎白卡 視障"},{"pid":"156c34ba26d261f3e3900f30a0a68dbbdf473f02","tid":2297343,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:38:20.000Z","msg":"想問下 1980x1080同2k有咩分別<br />\n我用緊31.5吋va曲面69ppi 165hz<br />\nmsi optix ag32c"},{"pid":"d39a919cba1d76332ad9f03b50f08361989758a5","tid":2297343,"uid":130320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:39:54.000Z","msg":"27吋真係無謂4K<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"24ce8dc4c20a96d678ab5efaf744bfa408e8c5b8",